task.summary:
Commit 02 -
Testing VCS Control with Webstorm

Commit 05
Bootstrap Basic Template has been successfully integrated for all non-dashboard purposes.

Commit 07 - Script Documented
The JavaScript controller defined till now were properly documented for ease in future use.

Commit 08 - Global Variables declared
All global variable are now declared in a service in order to keep code and data separate.

Commit 09 - Dashboard Automation Started
The automation and centralized generation of dashboard using the Angular Template renderings and Directives has been started. Integration on several levels is taking place.

Commit 10 - Dashboard Automation Complete
Dashboard automation using Anlar is complete. View refactoring to begin.

Commit 11 - Tests for the top navigation bar complete
All tests for the top navigation bar are complete. The development of backend begins simultaneously.

Commit 14 - Routing successfully tested
Routing of views was successfully tested.

Commit 15 - Views created
Views were successfully created.

Commit 16 - URL based routing implemented
Basic routing is implemented.

Commit 18 - Front end working fine.
Front end with basic routing is working fine. Work on revamping the signin mechanism begins.

Commit 20 - JWT across CORS using AngularJS tested successfully.
JWT tokens were created and tested to be working fine in AngularJS.

Commit 21 - UI Changes on the Signin Page.
Rounded corners implemented on the signin page. Also, the edges for the button have been smoothened. Work on full fledged authentication mechanism begins!
